casebody.data:
MISCELLANEOUS ORDERS

2007-0683. In re Application of Holbrook.

Board of Commissioners on Character and Fitness, No. 338. On June 11, 2007, applicant, Melinda Long Holbrook, filed with this court a motion to maintain original board papers under seal. Upon consideration thereof,

It is ordered by the court that the motion is granted. The record in this case, the report of the board, and all documents filed in this ease shall be maintained permanently under seal.
